neuronResources.note: In the original morphology file, the reconstruction is upside down: the pia is at the bottom and the white matter at the top.

As of January 2015, we became aware that the database contained a duplicated reconstruction file of this same neuron, named B8-26. The latter duplicate is no longer available since version 6.2. For any question or clarification, please contact us
